channel.title: Xfire SERVER HELP

Anyone on the forums who has xfire and is willing to help me with my server, or even if you just have advice, please post... There are a few specific things that i need help with, that aren't able to be quickly solved using this forum at the moment. TY if you help or post. I want to start a group of xfire users who can all help each-other and other people on the forums who need help Email= kayauts@yahoo.com Xfire= Kayauts (will show up as Лорд пирога) AIM= kayauts (Note: I do not use AIM very often)
(server is "kayautscape.no-ip.org") Not usually up, but will be after some issues have been worked out.
